title: Lincoln Home National Historic Site: Amphibians
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Nature     Animals     Amphibians                Amphibians         Wood Frog unknown photo  The lack of any riparian areas in the park exclude many species of Amphibians. When walking through Lincoln Home National Historic Site at night you will occasionally hear Tree Frogs singing from the brush and trees which are interspersed throughout the historic buildings.
